INSERT INTO industry_hub
                (
                    id,
                    name,
                    owner,
                    created_at,
                    updated_at
                )
                VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5)
                ON CONFLICT (id)
                DO UPDATE SET
                    name        = EXCLUDED.name,
                    updated_at  = EXCLUDED.updated_at
